      "fraction_vocabulary": "📖 Ṭhen biafang",
      "definitions_of_every_fraction_term_use": "K-8 math cachimhnak ah hmanmi ṭhen biafang paoh sullam, tahchunhnak he. Kawl khawh.",
      "search_vocabulary": "Biafang kawl...",
      "search_vocabulary_2": "Biafang kawl",
      "no_matches": "Aa tlakmi a um lo.",
      "iep_goal_bank_fraction_specific": "🎯 IEP Goal Bank — ṭhen kong lawng",
      "pre_formatted_smart_goals_for_iep_team": "IEP team caah a timhmi SMART goal. Goal pakhat cio nih CCSS standard ah aa pehtlaih, AlloFlow chungah hmasawnnak-zohkhenhnak data hmun a langhter, cun accommodation a fcommi a langhter. Na siangngakchia caah copy law remh.",
      "show_accommodations_and_progress_monit": "Accommodation le hmasawnnak zohkhenhnak langhter",
      "progress_monitoring": "Hmasawnnak zohkhenhnak: ",
      "copy_goal_to_clipboard": "📋 Goal clipboard ah copy",
      "all_lesson_plans": "← Lesson plan dihlak",
      "learning_objectives": "🎯 Cawnnak sullam",
      "lesson_plan_templates": "📚 Lesson plan template",
      "ready_to_use_micro_units_3_5_days_each": "Ṭhen topic fommi caah a si khawhmi micro-unit (ni 3-5 fatuk). Plan pakhat cio nih tuahnak kha Fraction Lab tab ah aa pehtlaih, cucaah demo asiloah pek khawh.",
      "where_do_fractions_come_from": "Ṭhen cu khoin dah a rat?",
      "the_earliest_fraction_notation_dates_t": "Ṭhen ṭialnak a hmasa bik cu Egypt hlanlio kum 1800 BCE hrawng ah a rat. Egypt mi nih \"unit fraction\" lawng an hman — nambat cung 1 a ngeimi lawng (1/2, 1/3, 1/4 bantuk). Ṭhen dang paoh cu unit fraction telhnak in an ṭial: 2/5 = 1/3 + 1/15. Tuchan bar ṭialnak (nambat cung, nambat tang cung ah) cu kum 1200 CE hrawng ah Arab mathematician sinin a rat.",
      "where_do_the_fraction_words_come_from": "Ṭhen biafang cu khoin dah a rat?",
      "numerator_comes_from_the_latin_numerar": "\"Numerator\" cu Latin \"numerare\" (rel) in a rat — ṭhen zeizat timi a rel. \"Denominator\" cu \"denominare\" (min sak) in a rat — ṭhen a nganzia a min sak. Aa tlangin: nambat tang nih ṭhen phun a min sak; nambat cung nih cu ṭhen zeizat na ngeih timi a rel.",
      "the_decimal_point": "Decimal point",
      "decimals_as_we_know_them_were_populari": "Tuchan decimal cu Simon Stevin nih kum 1585 ah a cauk \"De Thiende\" (The Tenth) ah a langhter. A hlanah cu nambat-a-dih-lo langhter awkah ṭhen lawng a um. Decimal point cu kum 1700 hna ah lawng vawlei pumpi in an cohlan.",
      "what_does_percent_mean": "Percent sullam cu zeidah a si?",
      "percent_comes_from_the_latin_per_centu": "\"Percent\" cu Latin \"per centum\" — \"za khat ah\" in a rat. Cucaah 25% cu 25 per 100, asiloah 25/100 timi a si. % hmelchunhnak cu kum 15 (15th-century) Italy dawr ṭialnak i \"per c.\" tawinak in a chuak.",
      "what_is_a_reciprocal": "Reciprocal cu zeidah a si?",
      "the_reciprocal_of_a_b_is_b_a_flip_it_u": "a/b i reciprocal cu b/a a si — a bung tein letting. Ṭhen zero a si lomi paoh nih reciprocal a ngei. Ṭhen le a reciprocal pungnak cu zungzal 1 a si: (3/4) × (4/3) = 12/12 = 1. Cucaah ṭhen he kulhnak cu a reciprocal he pungnak he aa lo lo.",
      "why_is_1_2_the_most_used_fraction": "Zeicaah 1/2 cu ṭhen hmanmi a tam bik a si?",
      "1_2_is_the_most_common_fraction_in_eve": "1/2 cu nifate biafang ah ṭhen a tammi bik a si, zeicahtiah 0 le 1 karlak a lai taktak ah a um. Biafang in kan chimmi ṭhen lawng zong a si: \"cheh\" — \"pahnih chungah pakhat\" ti loin. Holh dang zong nih 1/3 le 1/4 caah biafang ṭhen an ngei (thumdanh, palidanh).",
      "pizza_is_mathematical": "Pizza cu mathematical a si",
      "a_pizza_is_a_perfect_fraction_model_be": "Pizza cu ṭhen model tlingtlang a si, zeicahtiah kual a si (cucaah peng paoh cu a lai in a chuak), peng cu rel a fawi, cun mathematical sullam taktak he aa tlak: ṭhen n/d cu aa lomi ṭhen a dihmi d chungin aa lomi ṭhen n a si.",
      "when_fractions_are_not_enough": "Ṭhen nih a tlin lo tikah",
      "some_numbers_like_and_2_cannot_be_writ": "Nambat cheukhat, π le √2 bantuk cu nambat a dihmi pahnih i ṭhen ah ṭial khawh a si lo. Cu hna cu irrational number an ti. Pythagorean hna (kum 500 BCE hrawng) nih √2 cu ṭhen ah ṭial khawh a si lo timi a langhtermi Hippasus mathematician kha an thah tiah an chim.",
      "continued_fractions": "Continued fraction",
      "any_real_number_can_be_written_as_a_co": "Real number zeihmanh cu \"continued fraction\" ah ṭial khawh a si — 1 + 1/(2 + 1/(2 + 1/(2 + ...))) bantuk aa hrungmi ṭhen. Hi nih ṭhen tahdawhnak a ṭha bik a pek. π ≈ 22/7 cu a hmasa bik term hna in; a ṭha deuh cu 355/113.",
      "fractions_in_music": "Music i ṭhen",
      "musical_pitch_ratios_are_fractions_the": "Music aw ratio cu ṭhen a si. Octave cu 2:1 ratio a si (frequency a i pahnih). Perfect fifth cu 3:2. Major third cu 5:4. Pythagoras nih nambat a dihmi ratio a fawimi nih aw a ṭhami a chuahter timi a hmuh.",
      "why_the_common_denominator": "Zeicaah nambat tang pumhmun?",
      "two_pizzas_can_only_be_combined_if_the": "Pizza pahnih cu peng a nganzia aa lomi ah at asile lawng aa kawh khawh. Nambat tang aa lo lomi = peng a nganzia aa lo lomi = aa kawh khawh lo. Nambat tang pumhmun cu \"peng aa lomi\" timi taktak a si.",
      "baseball_stats_are_fractions": "Baseball stat cu ṭhen a si",
      "a_batting_average_like_333_means_1_3_o": "Batting average .333 bantuk cu at-bat 1/3 nih hit a chuahter timi a si. Pitcher ERA, on-base percentage, slugging percentage — vialte cu ṭhen an si. Baseball cu hi bantuk statistical ruahnak a langhter hmasa bikmi thawhlehnak a si, kum 1850 hna ah a thawk.",
      "cuisenaire_rods": "Cuisenaire rod",
      "georges_cuisenaire_was_a_belgian_prima": "Georges Cuisenaire cu kum 1950 hna i Belgium primary saya a si, ṭhen tel in nambat pehtlaihnak ngakchia hna theihhngilhter awkah a saumi 1 in 10 rod a rakmi a chuahtu a si. Classroom tampi ah na hmuhmi \"fraction wall\" cu amah rod taktak i digital thlah a si.",
      "fractions_in_ancient_china": "China hlanlio i ṭhen",
      "the_chinese_mathematical_text_nine_cha": "China math cauk \"Nine Chapters on the Mathematical Art\" (kum 100 BCE hrawng) nih ṭhen arithmetic a tel, tuchan kan cawnmi he mathematical thawng aa lomi nambat tang pumhmun hmuhnak lam zong a tel.",
      "computers_and_fractions": "Computer le ṭhen",
      "computers_store_decimal_fractions_in_b": "Computer nih decimal ṭhen kha binary ah a chiah. Decimal 0.1 cu binary ah dik tein langhter khawh a si lo — base 2 ah aa cangṭhanmi ṭhen ah a cang. Cucaah 0.1 + 0.2 cu programming language cheukhat ah 0.30000000000000004 tiin a chuak.",
      "fraction_adjacent_sayings": "🗣 Ṭhen he aa pehtlaihmi biafang",
      "dogs_spend_about_1_2_their_lives_sleep": "Uico nih an nunnak 1/2 hrawng an ih. Kum 12 a rammi uico cu kum 6 hrawng a ih cang.",
      "cats_sleep_about_2_3_of_every_day_that": " Minu nih nifate 2/3 hrawng an ih. Cu cu nikhat ah suimilam 16.",
      "elephants_drink_about_1_8_of_their_bod": "Vohpi nih nikhat ah a puk rithlawhnak 1/8 hrawng ti a din. Vohpi pound 12,000 nih ti pound 1,500 a din!",
      "a_blue_whale_s_tongue_weighs_about_1_2": "Blue whale a lei cu maw tehte 1/2 hrawng a rithlawh (~pound 6,000).",
