      "my_child_says_i_hate_fractions": "Ka fapa/fanu nih \"Ṭhen ka hua\" a ti",
      "very_common_fractions_break_the_rules_": "A tam tukmi a si. Ṭhen nih nambat a dihmi caah siangngakchia an cawnmi phunglam a phih — nambat a nganmi nih zungzal a man a nganmi timi a si lo. Thinhunnak cu taktak le a hmaan a si. Bawmh awkah: (1) pizza asiloah fraction strip bantuk a langmi model hman, (2) nunphung taktak he pehtlaih (rawlṭhennak, caan, tangka), (3) tlawm te sawhsawh practice (nikhat ah min 5) a saumi session lo in, (4) zuamnak lawmhpiak, lehnak dik lawng si loin.",
      "my_child_doesn_t_understand_why_proced": "Ka fapa/fanu nih ZEICAAH procedure a ṭuan timi a hngalh lo",
      "they_are_not_alone_most_students_learn": "An tuar bal lo a si lo — siangngakchia tampi nih procedure hmasa ah an cawn, zeicaah timi cu a hnu ah. Bawmh awkah procedure kha lim he zeitindah a lang timi zungzal langhter. \"3/4 kha 1/2 he pung\" cu rectangle in ṭial khawh. Op Proofs tab nih na caah a tuah. \"Zeicaah?\" timi kha nemnak he tam tein hal.",
      "how_can_i_help_with_homework_without_d": "An caah tuah piak loin homework zeitin dah ka bawmh khawh?",
      "use_the_worked_examples_tab_they_show_": "Worked Examples tab hman — ruahnak he kal hnu kal procedure a langhter. Aa lomi harnak aa tlang in kal hnu, cu khat taktak si loin. \"Zeitin thawk timi ka hngalh lo\" an ti ahcun, \"Harnak nih zeidah hmuh awk a ti? Zeidah kan hngalh cang?\" ti in hal. Word Problems i hint system nih hint aa bunmi a pek — lehnak hlanah a hmasa bik zoh.",
      "what_should_i_drill": "Zeidah drill awk a si?",
      "ies_practice_guide_recommends_1_magnit": "IES Practice Guide nih: (1) a nganzia-ruahnak (number line rian), (2) a langmi le hmelchunhnak karlak pehtlaihnak, (3) context i word problem. HLIH AWK: hngalhthiamnak um lo in procedure drill. Benchmark Trainer ah min 5, Word Problems ah min 5, lentecelhnak ah min 5 hman — cu cu min 15 session ṭha bik a si.",
      "my_child_gets_the_procedure_right_but_": "Ka fapa/fanu nih procedure a dik nain lehnak a sual",
      "usually_means_a_small_arithmetic_error": "Cu cu arithmetic sual tete (tahchunh, a hmaan lo in pung) asiloah a fawi lo timi a si. Cheat Sheet langhter — an rian kha kal hnu kal in an check khawh. Lam dang in dik maw ti fehnak (hmasa ah tahdawh, asiloah model dang hman) ceih.",
      "what_if_i_don_t_remember_fractions_wel": "Ṭhen kha keimah nih ka hngilh chih ahcun zeidah?",
      "you_don_t_have_to_be_the_expert_use_th": "Thiammi na si a herh lo! Tab Guide le Worked Examples hman — procedure fiang tein an chim. A ṭha deuh: \"aa tlang in ceih u sih\" ti in langhter. Na fapa/fanu he na cawn ṭi khawh. Vocabulary tab cu mi upa caah zong a bawmh.",
      "how_do_i_know_if_my_child_is_on_track": "Ka fapa/fanu cu lam ah maw ti zeitin ka hngalh?",
      "look_at_the_standards_tab_to_see_which": "An grade caah an hngalh awkmi CCSS standard zoh awkah Standards tab zoh. Mastery tab nih hmasawnnak a langhter. Check rang caah: (a) 3/4 model an ṭial khawh maw, (b) 1/2 he aa lomi ṭhen an chim khawh maw, (c) 2/3 le 3/4 tahdawh law an fianter khawh maw? Cu tahnak thum nih K-5 ṭhen ruahmi a tam bik a huap.",
