      "attack_time_to_reach_full_volume_decay": "Attack: volume a khatnak tlin awkah caan. Decay: sustain tiang a nuamnak caan. Sustain: volume level a mancakmi. Release: key na chuah hnu ah a thi awkah caan.",
      "a_scale_is_an_ordered_set_of_pitches_m": "Scale cu pitch a remhmi pawl an si. Modes cu degree phundang in a thawkmi scale rotation an si. Pakhat cio nih lungthin ruahnak dang a ser.",
      "chords_are_built_by_stacking_intervals": "Chords cu interval (3rds) khan hlan in ser an si. Major nih major 3rd + minor 3rd a hman. Minor nih a leng. Extended chords nih 7ths, 9ths le a tam deuh an chiah.",
      "kicks_use_a_sine_oscillator_with_a_pit": "Kicks nih pitch sweep a ngeimi sine oscillator an hman. Snares nih noise (filtered) + tone body an pehtlaih. Hi-hats nih high-pass filtered noise bursts an hman.",
      "4_4_4_quarter_note_beats_per_bar_most_": "4/4 = bar pakhat ah quarter-note beats 4 (a tam bikmi). 3/4 = waltz ruahnak. 6/8 = compound duple. 5/4 le 7/8 nih grooves aa lawmlomi, ram dang an ser.",
      "keys_arranged_by_ascending_5ths_clockw": "Keys cu clockwise in a kaimi 5ths in remh an si. A naih keys nih note 7 chungin 6 an rualh. Clockwise in kal nih sharps a chiah; a lettu ah flats a chiah.",
      "every_musical_sound_contains_overtones": "Music aw paoh nih fundamental cung ah overtones a ngei. An thazang relative nih timbre a khiah — cucaah trumpet nih flute he pitch pakhat ah a dang in aa theih.",
      "an_interval_is_the_distance_between_tw": "Interval cu pitch pahnih karlak hlat a si, semitones in tahmi a si. Frequency ratio nih consonance a khiah (3:2 bantuk ratio a fawimi cu a nem in aa theih).",
      "plays_chord_notes_one_at_a_time_in_seq": "Chord note pawl kha pakhat cio in remh in a tuk. A cung = a niang in a sang, A niang = a sang in a niang. Chords a dinmi in a luangmi pattern a ser.",
      "a_filter_removes_frequencies_above_low": "Filter nih cutoff frequency a cungah (lowpass), a niangah (highpass), asiloah a kulh ah (bandpass) frequencies a hlonh. Resonance (Q) nih cutoff a naih frequencies a karh i peak a ser.",
      "tremolo_periodic_volume_changes_amplit": "Tremolo: caan tluk in volume thlennak (amplitude modulation). Vibrato: caan tluk in pitch thlennak (frequency modulation). A pahnih in LFO (Low Frequency Oscillator) nih an uk.",
      "discovered_in_1983_a_noise_burst_feeds": "1983 ah hmuh a si. Noise burst nih feedback a ngeimi delay line a tawi tukmi ah a lut. Delay time nih pitch a khiah. Feedback loop chungah filter nih ceunak le decay a uk. Plucked strings kha a taktak in a i chuah.",
      "the_sequencer_is_a_composition_tool_ea": "Sequencer cu composition tool a si. Step pakhat cio nih beat subdivision a langhter. Melody row nih pitched notes a chiah, drums nih rhythm a chiah. Musical notation nih na sermi a langhter.",
