      "olympus_mons_on_mars_is_21_9_km_high_n": "Mars i Olympus Mons cu 21.9 km a sang — Everest nakin voi 3 tluk!",
      "neptune_s_winds_reach_2_100_km_h": "Neptune thli cu 2,100 km/h a phan!",
      "earth_s_magnetic_field_deflects_charge": "Vawlei magnet hmun nih ni in a rami charge thil a hlonh. Ozone nih UV a bawmh, asinain magnetosphere cu venhimnak biapi bik a si!",
      "the_iau_s_2006_definition_requires_pla": "IAU 2006 bianabia nih planet nih an kulhnak lam kha thil dang in an thianter awk a duh.",
      "also_called_the_goldilocks_zone_not_to": "\"Goldilocks zone\" tiin zong an ti — a cung ah ti tui a um khawh nakah a lum tuk lo, a dai tuk lo.",
      "the_moon_rotates_exactly_once_per_orbi": "Thla cu kulh khat ah voikhat a hei — hi i tlaihnak cu kum bilian tampi chung tikulh thawnnak ruangah a si.",
      "opportunity_rover_found_hematite_blueb": "Opportunity rover nih hematite \"blueberry\" a hmuh — ti chungah lawng a chuakmi lung. Van in hmanthlak nih liva delta hlun a langhter!",
      "venus_is_hotter_462_c_vs_430_c_mercury": "Venus a lum deuh (462°C, 430°C he tahchunh)! Mercury cu lumnak tlaih awk van thli a ngei lo. Greenhouse effect cu hlatnak nakin a biapi deuh.",
      "gas_giants_have_no_solid_surface_they_": "Gas giant cu a cung khak a ngei lo! Hydrogen le helium gas an si i laili lam ah a ttha chin. Probe cu a dong lo in a tla lai.",
      "earth_s_distance_from_the_sun_doesn_t_": "Ni in Vawlei hlatnak cu ni khat chungah a thleng lo. Sunlei ti cu Ni cu na van ah a sang bik ti sullam a si. January ah Vawlei a naih bik (perihelion)!",
      "jupiter_is_11x_wider_than_earth_and_1_": "Jupiter cu Vawlei nakin voi 11 a kau i, a chungah Vawlei 1,300 a lut khawh! Solar system chungah ngannak cu a i dang tuk.",
      "pluto_is_still_in_the_solar_system_it_": "Pluto cu solar system ah a um rih! 2006 ah \"planet\" in \"dwarf planet\" ah an thleng nain, Ni a kulh rih.",
      "the_asteroid_belt_is_mostly_empty_spac": "Asteroid kulh cu hmun a hoihmi a tam bik! Asteroid karlak hlatnak cu km milian tampi a si. Vantlangkuang cu ttihnak um lo in a luan khawh.",
      "not_always_saturn_is_95x_earth_s_mass_": "Zeitikcia hmanh si lo! Saturn cu Vawlei nakin voi 95 a rit nain a cung gravity cu 1.06g lawng a si, a ngan tuk i a rithau a tlawm ruangah. Rithau cu rithau LE a kau he a i pehtlai.",
      "all_parts_of_the_moon_receive_sunlight": "Thla cheu vialte nih ni ceunak an hmuh! \"A hlat lei\" cu tidal locking ruangah Vawlei in kan hmuh khawh lomi a cheu lawng a si. Ni cu a tluk in a hmuh.",
      "the_habitable_zone": "Nunnak Hmun",
      "the_habitable_zone_or_goldilocks_zone_": "Nunnak hmun (asiloah \"Goldilocks zone\") cu arfi in hlatnak, planet a cung ah ti tui a um khawhnak hmun a si. Kan solar system ah Venus cu a chung donghnak ah a um, Vawlei cu laili ah a um, Mars cu a leng donghnak ah a um. Asinain ti tui ngeih awkah van thli le magnet hmun ttha zong a herh!",
      "the_greenhouse_effect": "Greenhouse Effect",
      "when_sunlight_heats_a_planet_s_surface": "Ni ceunak nih planet a cung a lumter tikah, a cung nih lumnak (infrared) a chuahter. Greenhouse gas (CO₂, CH₄, H₂O) nih hi lumnak hi a la i a chuahter tthan, cutin planet kha a lumter. Vawlei greenhouse cu +33°C a si (nunnak a tha). Venus mi cu +510°C (dinlo). Mars nih a ngei loin a si (-60°C). Greenhouse gas zeizat a um timi nih a donghnak a khiah!",
      "magnetic_shields": "Magnet Venhimnak",
      "a_planet_s_magnetic_field_creates_a_ma": "Planet magnet hmun nih \"magnetosphere\" a ser — hmuh khawh lomi venhimnak, ni thli (Ni in a rami charge thil) a hlonhtu. Vawlei magnetosphere nih kan van thli a venh i nunnak a si khawhter. Mars nih kum bilian 4 hlan ah a magnet hmun a hlawh i, a van thli tlawmte in an la ta. Jupiter magnetosphere cu Vawlei mi nakin voi 20,000 a ttha deuh!",
      "why_isn_t_pluto_a_planet": "Zeicah dah Pluto cu Planet a si lo?",
      "in_2006_the_international_astronomical": "2006 ah International Astronomical Union nih planet caah bia pathum a khiah: (1) Ni a kulh ✓, (2) A luan awkah rithau a tlin ✓, (3) A kulhnak lam kha thil dang in \"a thianter\" ✗. Pluto cu a kulhnak hmun kha Kuiper Belt thil thongkhat tampi he an i chunhkhawm, cucaah \"dwarf planet\" tiah an ti. Hi ruangah a lawmhawk a si lo ti a si lo — New Horizons nih a rian a tuah rih ti a langhter!",
      "tidal_locking": "Tidal Locking",
      "over_billions_of_years_gravitational_t": "Kum bilian tampi chungah gravity tikulh ttthanak nih thla heinak kha a ttihter i a kulh caan he a i tluk. A donghnak: hmai pakhat lawng cu planet lei ah a hmai peng. Kan Thla cu Vawlei he a i tlaih. Mercury cu Ni he a cheu lawng in a i tlaih (3:2). Pluto le Charon cu an i tlaih tawn — hmai khat lawng an i hmuhter peng!",
      "searching_for_life": "Nunnak an hawl",
      "a_biosignature_is_any_evidence_of_past": "Biosignature cu hlanlio asiloah atu nunnak langhternak zeihmanh a si. Science mi nih an hawlmi: (1) ti tui, (2) organic molecule, (3) van thli ah oxygen asiloah methane bantuk gas, nunnak a ser lo ahcun a um kho lomi, (4) tha chuahnak hmun. Kan solar system ah hmun tha bik: Mars (ti hlun), Europa (vun tang tikulh), Enceladus (ti tuithlipi), le Titan (methane liva).",
