      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Holhchiannak widget — nambat a um lo, lehnak langhter a um lo, lehnak pek a um lo. Kepler III ning ah T = √(a³/M), M cu ni rithau, a cu AU, T cu kum. Perihelion / aphelion i v caah Vis-viva an hman.",
