      "from_walking_to_light_speed_log_scale_": "Kalnak in ceunak rannak tiang (log tahnak). Voyager 1 cu mi nih a sermi thil a hlat bik a si i a leng lam ah kan probe a rang bik hna chungah pakhat, asinain van tahchunh ah a ttih tuk rih.",
      "voyager_1_is_the_fastest_object_humans": "Voyager 1 cu vantlangkuang tahchunh ah a rang i atu ah mi nih a sermi thil a hlat bik a si, asinain arfi a naih bik phak awkah kum 80,000 hrawng a hman lai. Ceunak nih cu khualtlawnnak khi kum 4 in a dih.",
      "star_forming_region": "✨ Arfi Sernak Hmun",
      "watch_stars_form_from_cold_dust_to_hot": "Vutdai daimi in ni lum tiang arfi an cang ti zoh. Kum milian tlawmte chungah dinhmun 6.",
      "stars_are_born_in_clusters_from_giant_": "Arfi cu molecular vanmei ngan in bu tein an chuak. A vialte in: kum milian tlawmte. Tahchunhnak hmingthang: Orion Nebula (M42), Eagle Nebula (Pillars of Creation), Tarantula Nebula.",
      "big_cosmic_questions": "❓ Van Biahalnak Ngan",
      "10_of_the_deepest_open_questions_in_co": "Cosmology ah biahalnak a thuk bik le a hun rihmi 10. Cheukhat cu lehnak cheu an ngei; cheukhat cu thuhrukmi a si rih.",
