      "contrast_2": "Aa Dannak",
      "color_wheel_hsl_hsv_complementary_pair": "Rong Chakuang — HSL/HSV + aa remmi rong pahnih",
      "hue_0_360_around_the_wheel_saturation_": "Hue (chakuang kulh ah 0-360), saturation (rong a thiannak), lightness (a ceunak). Aa remmi cu a ralkhat ah an um, a naihmi cu a pawngah, triadic cu 120° in an i hlat. Newton nih 1666 ah rong vialte kha chakuang cungah a chiah.",
      "color_mixer_subtractive_vs_additive": "Rong Chawhtu — a i lakmi le a i telhmi",
      "paint_and_print_subtractive_cmy_mixes_": "Rong le cabu chuahnak = a i lakmi (CMY aa chawh tikah a thim); ceunak le computer hmai = a i telhmi (RGB aa chawh tikah a rang). Vawlei cu pakhat a si, sihmanhsehlaw nambat cu a dang tuk — printer nih K plate in a ruat, TV nih Hz in a ruat.",
      "pixel_art_bitmap_craft_at_8_8_to_32_32": "Pixel Milem — 8×8 in 32×32 tiang bitmap sernak",
      "each_pixel_is_a_deliberate_decision_ne": "Pixel pakhat cio cu ruah in a chiahmi bia khiahnak a si. NES sprites nih hero pakhat kha rong pali lawng he 16×16 chungah an chiah khawh. Bresenham lam sernak nih nambat kehkhat hmang lo in aa kawimi lam a suai.",
      "symmetry_reflection_rotation_glide": "Aa Tluk Tawknak — thlalang, vaknak, le a i hnawhnak",
      "bilateral_mirror_rotational_n_fold_poi": "Pahnih lam (thlalang), vaknak (n-fold), le point. Wallpaper phun 17 nih 2D milem aa cang ttheumi vialte kha an ṭhen khawh — Escher rian vialte cu mah a si.",
      "spirograph_hypotrochoid_roulettes": "Spirograph — hypotrochoid roulettes",
      "a_small_circle_rolls_inside_a_big_one_": "Aa lomi hmete cu a nganmi chungah a vak i, cacuang cu a laipi in a hlat. Radius pahnih ratio nih pangpar zat a khiah; cacuang hlatnak nih a thanzat a khiah. Hi ei-nawmnak thil hi 1965 ah ser a si, sihmanhsehlaw nambat cu 1700 kum in a rat.",
      "generative_algorithm_randomness_as_art": "Amah in Sernak — algorithm + hngalh lomi cu milem sertu a si",
      "sol_lewitt_wrote_instructions_the_wall": "Sol LeWitt nih hruainak lawng a ṭial; innka ah rian a ṭuanmi nih a tuah. Nihin: Processing, p5.js, Cinder. “Milem sertu cu phunglam a si, a chuak mi a si lo.”",
      "spin_art_centripetal_physics_in_paint": "Vaknak Milem — rong chungah laipi lam thawhnak physics",
      "drop_paint_spin_watch_it_fling_outward": "Rong ttum, vak ter, cun a leng lam ah vakin a i thehnak kha zoh. Damien Hirst nih vaknak milem zuar in tangka tampi a hmuh. Salad kuang a vaktu bantuk physics a si; F = mω²r.",
      "string_art_curves_from_straight_lines": "Hri Milem — lam a dingmi in a kawimi lam",
      "connect_every_n_th_nail_an_envelope_cu": "Nail N nak cio kha pehtlaih; envelope kawinak a chuak. Mary Everest Boole nih 1900 hrawng ah sianginn nambat cawnnak ah a chiah. Lam a dingmi in a chuakmi cardioid cu tuchan tiang ah a dawh.",
      "op_art_fooling_the_visual_system": "Op Art — hmuhnak lam hlennak",
      "bridget_riley_s_moir_fields_vasarely_s": "Bridget Riley moiré hmun, Vasarely grid. Thluak chungah nithlanak a hmuhtu cell hna cu aa dannak a rangtein aa thlen tikah an ṭuan tuk — cabu cu *a ṭhinlau* bantuk in a langh.",
      "tessellation_the_17_wallpaper_groups": "Tessellation — wallpaper phun 17",
      "every_periodic_2d_tiling_fits_one_of_1": "Aa cang ttheumi 2D tiling vialte cu aa tluk tawknak phun 17 chungah pakhat ah an i tel. Escher nih 1936 ah Alhambra a va zoh tikah hi kha a hngalh; cun kum 30 chung a phunphun kha a i zoh dih.",
      "fractal_self_similar_at_every_scale": "Fractal — a zauzat kip ah amah he aa lo",
      "mandelbrot_1975_cauliflower_coastlines": "Mandelbrot 1975. Cauliflower, tikulh kam, thi hri, khuapi, hnathlak — vialte hi fractal an si. “Khuazing cu bawrbal an si lo, tlang cu kon an si lo, thingkuang cu a nem lo.”",
      "gradient_smooth_color_transitions": "Gradient — rong a nem tein a thlennak",
      "css_gives_you_linear_radial_and_conic_": "CSS nih linear, radial, le conic gradient a in pek. Van chakuang taktak cu rong a i pehmi a ngei (aa ṭhen ṭhenmi a um lo) — “van chakuang rong 7” cu Newton nih hla ruangah amah duhnak in a khiahmi a si.",
      "stereogram_3d_from_a_flat_page": "Stereogram — cabu a phaimi in 3D",
      "90s_magic_eye_craze_each_eye_sees_a_sl": "1990 kum Magic Eye lawmhnak. Mit pakhat cio nih milem a hnawh chuahmi kha an hmuh; na mit kha a dik tein na chawh asiloah na ṭhen ahcun, thluak nih an pehtlaih i a thuknak a langhter. Mi 5% cu hmuh an khawh taktak lo — an sualnak a si lo.",
      "contrast_wcag_4_5_1_3_1_apca": "Aa Dannak — WCAG 4.5:1 / 3:1 / APCA",
      "wcag_2_1_normal_text_4_5_1_large_3_1_w": "WCAG 2.1: ca hmete 4.5:1, ca nganmi 3:1. Aa dannak a tlawm tikah mit a fak lomi hna caah zeicah a har — nangmah nih na rel khawh hmanhah. APCA (WCAG 3.0 a hnu deuh) nih mit nih a hmuhmi ceunak a hmang, luminance ratio lawng a si lo.",
      "harmony_lab_title": "Aa Remnak — aw, ratio, le rong",
      "harmony_lab_hint": "Aw aa remmi le aa rem lomi interval kha tahchunh, frequency ratio kha milem he pehtlaih, cun hla pehtlaihnak kha hmuhnak aa remnak ah thlen.",
